        sage.: desolve_laplace(de(f(x)),[f,x],[0,1,2])  ## IC option does not work
         #x*%e^x*(?%at('diff('f(x),x,1),x=0))-'f(0)*x*%e^x+'f(0)*%e^x

    AUTHOR: David Joyner (1st version 1-2006, 8-2007)
    """
